biography: Tommy is a formidable golfer known for his strategic mind and unwavering focus on the course. Although he maintains a calm exterior, those who know him well can attest to his fiery competitive spirit.

Hailing from Espoo Ringside Golf, Tommy is preparing to make his third appearance at the Hector Trophée in 2025. While he has yet to capture the coveted Hector Trophée or the Victor Trophy, Tommy's dedication and improving performance suggest that he is a strong contender to watch in the upcoming years.
His fellow competitors would be wise not to underestimate him.
